OL,3,CSix arrested in Carlisle murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FPolice have arrested six people in a
OL,7,Fmurder investigation, following the
OL,8,Fdeath of a man who was found with a
OL,9,Fserious head injury in Carlisle.
OL,11,FFour people were arrested on suspicion
OL,12,Fof murder and remain in police custody.
OL,14,FTwo further people were arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of causing grievous bodily
OL,16,Fharm with intent. They have both since
OL,17,Fbeen bailed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
