OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780589464
OL,3,CSix arrested in Carlisle murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to
OL,7,FWhinsmoor Drive in Carlisle at around
OL,8,F11:15am on Saturday 30 May, where a
OL,9,Fman in his 40s was airlifted to the
OL,10,FRoyal Victoria Infirmary in Newcastle.
OL,11,FHe was pronounced dead three days
OL,12,Flater, on Tuesday 2 June.
OL,14,FA cordon remains in place at the scene
OL,15,Fand Police say their investigations
OL,16,Fare continuing. They are urging anyone
OL,17,Fwith information to come forward.
OL,19,FOfficers say they would particularly
OL,20,Flike to hear from anyone in the area
OL,21,Fwith CCTV or dashcam footage.
